  <official_title>Randomized Phase II Trial of Pre-Operative Docetaxel-Cytoxan (TC) or Exemestane in Patients With Hormone Receptor-Positive Breast Cancers With Recurrence Scores Greater Than 10 (≥ 11) and Less Than 25 (≤ 24)</official_title>
